Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.28,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:18.89,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did I die again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:37.04,Konosuba_Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1523,1)}KONOSUBA\N{\fs16\c&H6900D2&}God's {\c&H0781E7&}Blessing {\c&H0F135A&}on {\c&H6900D2&}this {\c&H0781E7&}Wonderful {\c&H0F135A&}World{\c&H6900D2&}!
