Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:09.21,Konosuba_Ep_Number,Sign,0065,0000,0000,,Episode 7
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:09.21,Konosuba_Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}"A Second Death in This Freezing Season!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:56.42,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,After the battle with Verdia,\Na leader in the Devil King's army,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:58.38,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,the season turned to winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:02.64,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I groaned wholeheartedly, \Nas if I were coughing up blood:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.27,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I want money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.36,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Everyone wants that, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.76,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're entirely too unresourceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:16.57,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,You make a goddess like myself \Nsleep in a stable every single night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:19.45,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you ashamed of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.74,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand that, \Nthen give me more luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.70,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Spoil me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:29.54,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not get {\i1}why{\i0} I want more money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.58,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.33,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:35.79,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the debt you've racked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:38.15,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,most of the reward money we earn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:41.47,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,from every quest we do is \Ndeducted to repay those debts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.84,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Just this morning... Just this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:48.29,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,when I awoke in the straw of the stable,\Nmy eyelashes were frozen solid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:52.00,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep sleeping in that stable,\NI'm going to freeze to death for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.26,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:59.82,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,This city may have perished \Nin that battle with Verdia,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.53,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,if not for my super astounding efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.66,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,You should exalt me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.75,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,All of you should praise me, \Npraise me, and spoil me rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.71,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,You attention whore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.94,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,If your feats were {\i1}that{\i0} astounding,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:16.54,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,then the rewards, accolades, \N{\i1}and{\i0} debt are all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.05,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Pay off your debts on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.93,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:25.34,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for getting carried \Naway, so don't abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.43,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,Why all the fuss so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.06,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have some nice job lined up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.96,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,No, we haven't started looking for work yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.44,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Given the situation and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.85,Konosuba_Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.07,Konosuba_Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleeping at the inn. It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:44.44,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,The reward for fighting off a \Nleader in the Devil King's army
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:48.07,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,was distributed to every \Nadventurer who participated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:51.36,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for anyone to go \Nhunting dangerous winter monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.12,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,when their coin pouches are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:56.02,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I gladly welcome it, personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:58.18,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,S-So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:00.38,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,The stronger the enemy, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:03.38,Konosuba_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,KO-NO-SU-BA!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.80,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,The reward is well and good, but there \Nseriously aren't any decent quests...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.79,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma, Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:11.83,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.26,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:16.79,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,A kill quest for a pack of White Wolves. \NThe reward is a million eris!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:21.82,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagining a pack of wild \Nbeasts making a mess of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.41,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.46,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma, Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:26.23,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:27.79,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.12,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,A kill quest for a One-Shot Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:35.62,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time for me to \Nteach it which of us has
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:38.25,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,the stronger one-shot attack \Nwith my explosion magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:41.72,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I want nothing to do with a monster \Nwith such a dangerous-sounding name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:44.46,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we'd die instantly if it \Nso much as grazed our necks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.62,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,"The mobile fortress 'Destroyer' is approaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:52.27,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,so we are recruiting scouts to \Npredict the route it will take."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:56.22,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? What's a "Destroyer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:58.77,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,The Destroyer is the Destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.43,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,It's a massive fortress \Nthat moves at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:04.22,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,It lumbers around, trampling everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.53,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,It's oddly popular with children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.92,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:12.54,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.07,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,A Snow Sprite kill quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.38,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are Snow Sprites?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:22.11,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,They don't sound all that \Nstrong, based on the name,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.43,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,but it says the reward is 100,000 eris each.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:27.47,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of Snow \NSprites in the snowy plains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:31.75,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that spring will come half a \Nday sooner for every one you kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.40,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:34.86,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,They're very weak monsters, \Nso they're easily defeated, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:37.65,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,If we're accepting that \Nquest, I'll go get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.82,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.26,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,You're laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.86,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,Snow Sprites, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:48.60,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this masochistic crusader, \Nwho always wants to fight strong monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.06,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,look so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.95,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Still, money takes priority right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.16,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,These are Snow Sprites?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:06.02,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can't you do something \Nabout that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:09.37,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,You look like some dumb kid going \Ncicada-catching in the middle of winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:13.06,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I can catch Snow Sprites \Nwith this, and bottle them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.43,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I had the idea that if we mix \Nthem in with our drinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:20.62,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,we can have ice-cold drinks whenever we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.44,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Aren't I smart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.52,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I can see how this is going to play out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:27.24,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness, what happened to your armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.49,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be all right in that gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.00,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:36.62,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little cold, but that in itself is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:43.29,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I guess a pervert with steamy thoughts \Nhas a high body temperature to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:51.68,Kill_Quest_Header,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H25289F&}Kill Quest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:51.68,Kill_Quest_Body,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(698,1)}Kill the Snow Sprites!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:57.27,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Number three, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.27,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's darting all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.28,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:05.03,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I caught my fourth one! Kazuma, look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.04,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.37,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,If my kill count comes out too low,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.71,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill the Snow Sprites she caught, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.08,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:20.64,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.10,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.45,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I blow away all the ones in \Nthe area with explosion magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.92,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Wipe them all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.01,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.96,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,By my efflux of deep crimson,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.26,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,topple this white world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.10,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.34,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.57,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I got eight of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.70,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,That makes nine defeated Snow Sprites total.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.01,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,I even went up a level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.82,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nice going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:21.58,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been a little cooler if you \Nweren't buried in the snow, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.88,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.60,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Killing Snow Sprites is totally delectable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.71,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't everybody do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.34,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:32.90,Konosuba_Main,kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.90,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:40.92,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,So exciting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:44.82,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's playing dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:45.75,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:51.42,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you why adventurers don't \Naccept Snow Sprite kill quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:52.35,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:56.01,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,You lived in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:59.43,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sure you've at least heard the name \Nin the news and weather forecasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:02.18,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Snow Sprites' master,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.44,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,and is also said to evoke the image of winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:06.97,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.82,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,the Winter Shogun has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.57,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Winter Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:18.12,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,One of the specially designated monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.41,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,the country has put a huge bounty on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.90,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.60,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this monster plans \Nto use his position as shogun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.67,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,to have his way with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.25,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,I'll resist him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:33.01,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,but he will likely be beyond my \Ncapabilities, and I'll be shamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.01,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:39.77,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in this good-for-nothing world, \Nthe people, the food, and the monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:42.70,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,are all absolutely stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.80,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,M-My sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:09.39,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Sprites pick up the subconscious \Nthoughts of the people they encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:11.44,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,and take their form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.52,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,But the only ones strolling \Naround outside town
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:18.26,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,in winter are mostly just cheat-users\Nwho came here from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:21.20,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,So this guy was brought to life by some\Nidiot who came here from Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:25.16,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,whose train of thought associated \Nwinter with the Winter Shogun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.81,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:33.93,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,When this is over, I'm gonna step on the girl \Nwho's been playing dead this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.44,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.18,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:38.05,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,The Winter Shogun is generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.54,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,If we politely apologize, he'll overlook this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.83,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Prostrate yourself! \NProstrate yourself before him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.71,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone, toss your \Nweapons aside and bow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.97,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize! You hurry up \Nand apologize too, Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:03.06,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,The former-something-or-other who appears \Nto have abandoned all of her pride
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.65,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,prostrated herself quite \Nmagnificently, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.81,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry and bow your head, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.76,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,There may be nobody watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.73,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,but a knight such as myself would \Nnever bow her head to a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.82,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,You try to go off with monsters \Nwillingly all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:23.78,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show off your pointless \Npride only at times like these!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.24,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.52,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,You're forcing me to bow my \Nhead when I don't want to,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.39,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,and shoving my face into the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.00,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.44,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,What a reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.00,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,The snow is so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.58,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.45,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Your weapon, your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:43.78,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and throw down the \Nsword you're holding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.64,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:59.02,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I was killed by the Winter Shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.25,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Satou Kazuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.81,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:11.25,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,I am Eris, the goddess who will \Nlead you down a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:17.35,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Your life in this world is now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.47,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,This feels familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:27.70,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how it was when I met Aqua, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:32.23,Konosuba_Main,kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a goddess of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.91,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Satou Kazuma-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:39.38,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,you came all the way from \Npeaceful Japan to this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.15,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,only for this to happen to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.44,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:47.23,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Is she sincerely mourning my death?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.73,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,She's not like that useless goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.70,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Brave hero who came from a parallel world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.75,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.18,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,With my power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:59.73,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,I shall have you reincarnated in \Npeaceful Japan, to an affluent family,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:03.76,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,and will make sure you \Nlead a life of comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.01,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.80,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.51,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:12.07,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I-If possible, I'd like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:14.81,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,above-average parameters in\Ncharm, wisdom, and strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:18.40,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd be even happier in a life where \Na beautiful girl is my childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:21.07,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that is more than I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.86,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.70,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.84,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,but now it feels like I pulled \Nthrough by the skin of my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:32.06,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,This is a reward for trying my hardest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:35.08,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Because my life up to now had been so awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.57,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.38,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,I looked in on your life \Nfrom time to time myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.09,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your days were \Nfilled with adversity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.56,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:50.10,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I reincarnated thinking I'd get to go on \Na thrilling adventure, like in a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:53.10,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,This is like a misleading promo video, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.72,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,The useless goddess who came \Nwith me as a reincarnation perk
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:59.27,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,was just an arrogant good-for-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.10,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,We recruited allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.28,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,but the only ones who turned up were a crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.90,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,explosion girl who fell flat \Nevery time she used magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.40,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,and a masochistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.83,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,perverted crusader whose attacks always missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.38,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I was an adventurer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.91,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,but I did construction, side jobs, \Nand was forced into cabbage hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:20.46,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I was in debt deep enough to sell an \Norgan after defeating a boss enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:26.12,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping in the stables didn't restore my \Nstrength, it only froze me nearly to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.30,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how it feels to have your \Neyelashes frozen solid every morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:36.18,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,The previous world's game balance \Nwas beyond terrible, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.98,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.83,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.02,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,After you've been reborn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.47,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,may you be blessed once \Nmore with kind encounters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.36,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:09.55,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,It appears
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:14.72,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I was unexpectedly fond of \Nthat good-for-nothing world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.35,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,that I thought I hated...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:22.43,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to adventure with \Nthose girls a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.45,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Now, return to us, Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.28,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.48,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,How could you get killed off so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:31.30,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon for you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.66,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.24,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This voice... Aqua-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.79,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.97,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazuma, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.33,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I cast recovery magic on your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.61,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,so you can come back to this side now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.73,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.66,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.97,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,You've been reborn once already, \Nso according to the laws of Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.30,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,you can't be revived again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.54,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:55.82,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:59.16,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,She says that according to the \Nlaws of Heaven or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.93,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be revived again since \NI've been reborn once before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.43,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What goddess is spouting that nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.86,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Identify yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:12.71,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Where does a goddess in charge of a \Nbackwater like this get off talking to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:14.55,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,an elite in charge of Japan, that way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.33,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:20.41,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,The face of the goddess in charge \Nof that backwater is twitching now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.00,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.88,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,she's a goddess called "Eris"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.24,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Eris?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:29.42,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,The overrated Eris who's grown cocky \Nand even became a unit of currency,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.63,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,just because she's worshiped a little \Nin the established religion of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.93,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.40,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.31,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,If Eris gives you any more trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:39.34,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll confiscate her breast padsâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.56,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.20,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Pads?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.81,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,An exception! I'll deem this an exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.49,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open the gate right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.52,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,They're pads?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.74,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:48.65,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua-senpai is as unreasonable as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:48.65,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,They're really pads?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.03,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,KONOSUBA!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:50.65,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if they're pads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.21,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,You have now been connected \Nto the living world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.03,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,This normally never happens, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.16,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,You are called Kazuma-san, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.33,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, uh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:12.91,Konosuba_Main,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,This is our little secret, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:34.61,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,...zuma! Kazuma, please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.11,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.58,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're finally awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.73,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, that girl's so hard-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.33,Konosuba_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:50.06,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is kind of extremely embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:52.24,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on, Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:55.09,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,What're you blushing for? Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:18:00.28,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you back to life, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.37,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.35,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:09.23,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I want to trade this useless goddess \Nfor that cute goddess from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.54,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:14.97,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Like words of gratitude, or an apology \Nfor how you've treated such a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:17.02,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,high-class goddess with such \Ncontempt all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:19.24,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess change!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.53,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you damn NEET!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:26.25,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I send you to \Nmeet Eris right away, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.60,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now, now, calm down, Aqua!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.17,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.41,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel strange in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.30,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I'm all right for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.58,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.80,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,You were killed in such a \Nterrible way, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.62,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.12,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,H-How was I killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:48.36,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,You were beheaded by the Winter Shogun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.31,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite a splendid slice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.82,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,B-Beheaded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:00.82,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Winter in this world is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:05.14,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,a season where only those who make \Nit through the struggle for survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.67,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,despite the scarce food and harsh environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.71,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,are allowed to remain alive and active.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:14.97,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any quests beginners \Nlike us can complete easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.36,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.59,Kill_Quest_Body,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kill {\c&H050A4D&}T{\c&H2B4067&}he S{\c&HD9DBDC&}now Spri{\c&H0E175A&}tes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.59,Kill_Quest_Header,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1E2396&}Ki{\c&H131658&}ll Q{\c&H1E2396&}uest
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:20.59,Retired,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Retired
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.10,Konosuba_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,KONOSUBA!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:30.50,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.30,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,A Snow Sprite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:36.23,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't only prostrate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:40.25,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended to set them all \Nfree, but I saved just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:44.42,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even the Winter Shogun couldn't \Nsee through my convincing performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:46.24,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Aqua!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.19,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,All right, hand it over and I'll kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.56,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.36,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take this one home\Nand make it a refrigerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:56.17,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,The reward for killing those is 100,000 each!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.84,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.53,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I've already given it a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.12,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.33,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.55,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,She's resisting more than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.38,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,Let her be, Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.10,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.31,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll raise it with care,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:18.44,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,and when summer comes, \NI'll have it make lots of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.49,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll open a snow cone shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.76,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,We'll sleep together on hot, restless nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:26.59,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what does this little one eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:29.82,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Do Snow Sprites eat anything to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:32.66,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,They look so fluffy and soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.68,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,I bet if you put some sugar on it and took \Na bite, it'd actually be really tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.82,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I-I won't let you eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:41.65,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've worked up an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:43.51,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Let's order something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.52,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:49.39,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,That goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:53.31,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,She mourned my death so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:56.76,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,and smiled kindly when I was revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:02.36,Konosuba_Flashback,Eris,0000,0000,0000,,This is our little secret, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.86,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,A righteous, beautiful \Ngirl who's not an oddball!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:10.50,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, so long after I came to this world, the main heroine has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.82,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma, aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:13.58,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.17,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how much did you guys order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.80,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Once you become as great a magician as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.20,Konosuba_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,you require great sacrifices \Nin order to function.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:25.60,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.40,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:28.75,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you back to life today, Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:29.23,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.00,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with a \Nreward of this size, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:33.27,Konosuba_Main,Aqua,0000,0000,0000,,I put a little of the reward \Nfrom the quest into it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.98,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,That money was to get us through the winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.03,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:37.48,Konosuba_Main,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:40.07,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,If we run out of money, we can \Njust accept another quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:42.27,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of monster would be good next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:45.34,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe one that secretes a lot of slime,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:47.86,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,or one with repulsive tentacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.89,Konosuba_Main,Dark,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagining it makes me \Nquiver with excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:56.51,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, I should've\Nreincarnated in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.74,Konosuba_Italics,Kaz,0000,0000,0000,,I made the wrong choice...
